"active","activities","address","addressnumber","addressresponse","all","allowing","also","an","and","api","are","auth","available","background","better","boolean","buildingname","business","by","candidates","case","client","community","communitymanagerresponse","context","control","county","created","creation","current","currently","data","delius","display","district","documentation","dps","education","email","employment","endpoint","endpoints","existing","false","firstname","following","for","formats","from","gain","get","h1","hmpps","identifier","important","in","information","interfaces","is","json","lastname","lead","leaving","linked","main","manager","map","matching","nametyperequireddescriptionschema","need","nofixedabode","noms","none","number","of","offender","ok","openapi","opportunities","parameterintyperequireddescription","parameters","path","postcode","potential","prepare","prison","prisoner","prisonerid","probation","probation_api__prison_education__case_detail","profile","provide","pulls","readiness","reference","related","requests","required","requires","responses","returns","role","role_probation_api__prison_education__case_detail","roles","schemas","secured","service","statusdescriptionschema","streetname","string","supplied","swagger","system","systems","technical","that","the","these","this","to","together","town","true","ui","used","v1.0","with","work","yaml"],"pipeline":["trimmer"]}, "docs": {"11":{"title":"API Reference","content":"\n    \n    API Reference\n\n\n.technical-documentation \u003e h1 { display: none !important }\nThe following documentation is also available in these formats:\n\n\nOpenAPI JSON\nOpenAPI YAML\nSwagger UI\n\nAPI Reference v1.0\n\n\n\n\n\n\n/probation-case/{prisonerId}/main-address\n\nget\n\n  Get the current main address for a probation case\n\n\n  Accepts the prisoner identifier (NOMS number) and returns the \n            current main address linked to the probation case.\n            Requires PROBATION_API__PRISON_EDUCATION__CASE_DETAIL.\n\n\n\n\nParameters\n\n\nParameterInTypeRequiredDescription\n\n\n\n\nprisonerId\npath\nstring\ntrue\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nResponses\n\n\nStatusDescriptionSchema\n\n\n\n\n200\n\nOK\n\n\n\n{\n  \"buildingName\": \"string\",\n  \"addressNumber\": \"string\",\n  \"streetName\": \"string\",\n  \"district\": \"string\",\n  \"town\": \"string\",\n  \"county\": \"string\",\n  \"postcode\": \"string\",\n  \"noFixedAbode\": \"boolean\"\n}\n\n\n\nAddressResponse\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n/probation-case/{prisonerId}/community-manager\n\nget\n\n  Get the current active community manager for a probation case\n\n\n  Accepts the prisoner identifier (NOMS number) and returns the \n            currently active community manager of the probation case.\n            Requires PROBATION_API__PRISON_EDUCATION__CASE_DETAIL.\n\n\n\n\nParameters\n\n\nParameterInTypeRequiredDescription\n\n\n\n\nprisonerId\npath\nstring\ntrue\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nResponses\n\n\nStatusDescriptionSchema\n\n\n\n\n200\n\nOK\n\n\n\n{\n  \"firstName\": \"string\",\n  \"lastName\": \"string\",\n  \"email\": \"string\"\n}\n\n\n\nCommunityManagerResponse\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nSchemas\nAddressResponse\n\n\n\n\nNameTypeRequiredDescriptionSchema\n\n\n\n\nbuildingName\nstring\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\naddressNumber\nstring\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nstreetName\nstring\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\ndistrict\nstring\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\ntown\nstring\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\ncounty\nstring\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\npostcode\nstring\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nnoFixedAbode\nboolean\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\nCommunityManagerResponse\n\n\n\n\nNameTypeRequiredDescriptionSchema\n\n\n\n\nfirstName\nstring\ntrue\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nlastName\nstring\ntrue\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nemail\nstring\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","url":"/api-reference.html"},"13":{"title":"About","content":"Prison Education and Delius\nPrison Education is a DPS service that pulls together existing prisoner data related to activities and education, and also the creation of a work readiness profile for a prisoner. This profile is created and used by a Prison Education Lead to prepare an offender leaving prison to gain employment.\nBusiness Need\nTo provide the Prison Education system with background information from the probation systems, allowing better matching of candidates to potential work opportunities.\nContext Map\n\nInterfaces\nAPI Access Control\nAPI endpoints are secured by roles supplied by the HMPPS Auth client used in\nthe requests\n\n        \n          \nAPI Endpoint\nRequired Role\n\nAll\nROLE_PROBATION_API__PRISON_EDUCATION__CASE_DETAIL\n\n        \n      ","url":"/"}}}